---
source: tests/cli_help.rs
expression: stdout
---
Manage configuration

Usage: mf config [OPTIONS] [COMMAND]

Commands:
  schema  Show config schema
  show    Show effective config
  init    Initialize config file

Options:
      --root <PATH>      
      --config <PATH>    
  -v, --verbose...       
  -q, --quiet            
      --format <FORMAT>  [default: text] [possible values: text, json]
      --no-color         
  -h, --help             Print help
  -V, --version          Print version
